{"tid":2263680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母，大家真係要小心會員北角陳家樂","createTime":"2020-10-30T05:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T13:22:28.000Z","uid":344464,"like":119,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"4712ac9ccf5fa3a5c8c80bac9bbd8a042a4e3f42","tid":2263680,"uid":344464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:19:49.000Z","msg":"會員北角陳家樂#143343<br />\n<br />\n1.水鳩人送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家記住香港東南面個東沙島屬於台灣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2069332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2069332</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 扮去咗德國領事館<br />\n<br />\n去左德國領事館同領事解釋情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1207432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1207432</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/bkn-20190528103701028-0528_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190528%2Fbkn-20190528103701028-0528_00822_001.html&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=61adb512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/bkn-20190528103701028-0528_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n張圖原來係上東網搵嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.post舊圖fake鳩人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（突發）元朗鄉民準備用籐條插中國旗對付示威者！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1365968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1365968</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（突發）元朗鄉民準備用籐條插中國旗對付示威者！<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/aaMDKcV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/aaMDKcV</a><br />\n#13 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n仲要覆人&quot; 四小時前發 &quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人點會用個發字， 香港人淨係講法治...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.post 舊圖fake鳩人2<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n626 當日用上星期嘅圖，唆擺人去圍狗總<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YNzJUFa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYNzJUFa.png&h=f27baa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家小心山本一夫同mboli呢兩條友<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1259286\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1259286</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n更多資訊，可以喺呢個post入面睇<br />\n<br />\n 一路以為呢條友只係戇鳩仔, 而家發現原來可能唔係， 條友仲要成日上熱門， 大家真係要小心， 麻煩幫我推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68962116e2cf83cb8e46216ef8ba4573a44cfcb4","tid":2263680,"uid":344464,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:23:48.000Z","msg":"就算條友唔係對家嘅人， 條友都係好撚戇鳩，多次post假野水鳩人"},{"pid":"c29488bc1cde5dd960af743f9eda45d1846f7c5e","tid":2263680,"uid":344464,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:24:32.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫手推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27de3ec504ed54921943991a02ca4eddeae57666","tid":2263680,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:40:38.000Z","msg":"佢俾人bam咗？<br />\n個個post頭兩個reply都無咗？"},{"pid":"1ea790f94e291af0060c06f0711b43a4f478659d","tid":2263680,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee1d1d13b6f2354929df8c97e1352454204be30","tid":2263680,"uid":297981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0